## Skin Quiz — How It Works

Aliangé offers a free clinical skin analysis quiz at {{ shop.url }}/pages/quiz. The quiz asks 8 targeted questions covering baseline skin type, primary concern, tolerance to active ingredients, barrier integrity, structural ageing signs, congestion patterns, pigmentation status, and daily environment. Based on answers, a scoring engine developed by Dr. Alison Jamieson prescribes the most appropriate Aliangé protocol. Results are saved to the customer's profile via Klaviyo for personalised follow-up recommendations.

