## Collections

### All Products
Welcome to the complete Aliangé clinical skincare range. Developed by Dr. Alison Jamieson, bringing over 40 years of dermatological expertise, every formulation is grounded in rigorous scientific evidence. Products are designed to penetrate deeply, communicating with cells to regenerate, repair, and fortify the skin matrix.

**URL:** {{ shop.url }}/collections/all

### Skincare Protocols
At Aliangé, we believe in Protocols — structured, medically-inspired systems where every product is precisely calibrated to work in synergy. Formulated by Dr. Alison Jamieson, our protocols eliminate guesswork by delivering products in three phases: Prepare & Purify, Stimulate & Communicate, and Protect & Fortify. Targeting ageing, pigmentation, and breakouts.

**URL:** {{ shop.url }}/collections/protocols

### Clinical Serums
Serums formulated with smaller molecular weights to deliver highly concentrated active ingredients directly to the cellular matrix. Features cutting-edge biotechnology including DNA-repairing jellyfish peptides, barrier-fortifying sphingolipids, and brightening agent Oligopeptide-68.

**URL:** {{ shop.url }}/collections/serums

### Skincare Masques
Intensive treatment masques designed to accelerate skin recovery and fortification. Advanced biotechnology including probiotic complexes that restore the skin microbiome and potent antioxidants defending against environmental stressors. Recommended 2–3 times per week.

**URL:** {{ shop.url }}/collections/masques

### Cleansers & Exfoliators
Formulated with amino acids, coconut-derived surfactants, and precise AHA/BHA blends to prepare a balanced cellular canvas. Purifies without stripping the natural lipid barrier or disrupting the skin's acid mantle, maximising efficacy of subsequent actives.

**URL:** {{ shop.url }}/collections/cleanse

